Corning Glass Works said theexchange ratio for its previously announced acquisition ofHazleton Laboratories Corp has been established at 0.5165Corning common share for each Hazleton common share.    Corning said the prospectus regarding the merger isexpected to be mailed tomorrow to all Hazleton holders ofrecord February 18. Hazleton shareholders will vote on theproposed merger at a special meeting on March 31. Reuter&#3;